title: Rocket Power Season 1 (Ripped from Official DVD Release)
description:
===== WELCOME, FANS OF ROCKET POWER! =====
This torrent was created to provide fans of Rocket Power with the highest-quality versions of the episodes available.

They were converted from the official DVD release from Amazon using Handbrake's "Normal" preset with the CF option changed to 25 from its default of 20 to decrease the file sizes just a bit while still maintaining a high level of quality. Subtitles are also included!

NOTE: Episodes 21 and 22 from season 1 weren't included with the DVDs, for whatever reason.
